metadata.name: Crow Child [ENIGMA 001]
metadata.description:
The genesis piece of the Enigma series.. 

"Crow Child" 

a glitchy matrix between realities that evokes a sense of mystery and disorientation. This enigmatic piece invites viewers to delve into the eerie world of Enigma, where reality and fantasy collide, creating an immersive experience in the intriguing realm of the unknown.
